<div align="center"><center>

<table border="0" width="80%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%"><p align="center"><em><a name="howto"></a><font size="5" color="#80FFFF"><strong>--
    How to Play --</strong></font></em></p>
    <ul>
      <li><font color="#80FF80"><strong>GOAL --</strong></font></li>
    </ul>
    <blockquote>
      <p>Take away red balls as many as you can.</p>
    </blockquote>
    <ul>
      <li><font color="#80FF80"><strong>RULE --</strong></font></li>
    </ul>
    <blockquote>
      <p><font color="#FFFFFF">1. You can move the ball by jumping over another ball, and these
      balls </font><font color="#FFFF80"><strong>must be in line</strong></font><font
      color="#FFFFFF">.</font></p>
      <p><font color="#FFFFFF"><img src="help1.gif" width="78" height="80"
      alt="help1.gif (3905 bytes)"></font></p>
    </blockquote>
    <ul>
      <p>2. And then you have taken away a ball !!</p>
      <p><img src="help2.gif" width="78" height="80" alt="help2.gif (3787 bytes)"></p>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <li><font color="#80FF80"><strong>OPERATION --</strong></font></li>
    </ul>
    <blockquote>
      <ol>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">Click and drag the ball you want to move.</font></li>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">Move the ball to the place (hole) you want to put in.&nbsp; (The
          ball will follow your cursor now !)</font></li>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">Release the ball on the hole.</font></li>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">You will see the change !</font></li>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">Click &quot;UNDO&quot; and &quot;REDO&quot; anytime you want.
          (This game is not a matter of life and death. </font><font color="#FFFF80">:-)</font><font
          color="#FFFFFF"> )</font></li>
        <li><font color="#FFFFFF">Click the &quot;NEW GAME&quot; button anytime, and you can start a
          new game.&nbsp; (The hole will be chosen randomly.)</font></li>
      </ol>
      <p align="center"><font color="#FFFFFF">[ <a href="#game"><font face="Arial">Back to Game</font></a>
      ]</font></p>
    </blockquote>
    </td>
  </tr>
